Program: Omnibus
Title: In The Frosty Air
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376kh4
Last Broadcast Date: 09 December 1992
Memories of Christmas past in Lancashire and Yorkshire, in the Pennine Hills. Elderly people recall the christmas and New Year's Eves of their youth, recounting stories of the pleasures of the Christmas season which helped to make up for the hardships of the rest of the year.